high_descs: Move to the round black table so the fridge is on your right.
Pick up the sharp knife closest to you.
Turn right and carry the knife to the stove.
Place the knife in the pan on the back left burner.
Pick up the pan with the knife in it.
Carry the pan and knife to the kitchen table, but this time the fridge will be behind you and two heads of lettuce directly in front of you.
Place the pan with the knife in it on the table behind the left head of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Move a pan under a knife on the table.

high_descs: Go forward a few feet before turning left towards a black, round table
Pick up the sharp knife just to the left of the lettuce
Turn around and move a few feet before turning left towards the stove
Place the knife, point down in the pan behind the kettle sitting on the stove
Pick up the pan with the knife
Turn around and move in between the table and the safe before turning left towards the table.
Put down the pan with the knife to the left of the left most lettuce
anns.task_desc: Placing a pan with a knife pointed down in it upon a dinner table

high_descs: Take about three steps forward then turn left to face the black table.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that's near the head of lettuce near you.
Turn around and walk to the stove that's on your left.
Put the knife in the pan that's on the left rear burner.
Pick up the pan with the knife in it.
Turn left and walk to the chair then take a step to your right then a step forward then turn left.
Put the pan above the head of lettuce on your left.
anns.task_desc: Put a frying pan with a knife in it on the table.

high_descs: Walk forward to the middle of the room and then turn to the table to your left
Grab a knife next to the lettuce
Turn around walk forward and then turn left to face the stove.
Place the knife on top of the second stove on the left.
Pick up the cooking top on top of the second stove on the left.

Turn to your left and walk forward until you reach the table then turn right walk towards the white cabinet and then turn left again and walk towards the end of the room, turning left again to face the table.
Walk to the table and place the plate in front of the right top corner of the Lettuce to your left.
anns.task_desc: Grab a knife and a cooking pot from the kitchen and place them on the table.

high_descs: Walk forward then turn left to the black table.
Pick up the knife next to the lettuce that is closest.
Turn around, go to the stove top on the left.
Put the knife in the pan on the back left burner.
Take the pan from the stove top.
Turn left, walk towards the safe, turn to the left to face the black table.
Put the pan on the table on the left side above the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a knife on a table.

high_descs: Walk towards the fridge and turn right to the round table.
Pick up the knife by the lettuce.
Turn right and walk forward to the cupboard then turn left to the stove.
Put the knife in the pan directly behind the kettle.
Pick up the pan with the knife in it.
Turn left and walk toward the round table then turn right to face the fridge, then turn left again to face the round table.
Place the pan with the knife in it on the round table behind the leftmost head of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with a knife in it on the round table behind the lettuce.
